#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.214"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.214:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.214:0.2"
msgid "22. Akkosakavagga"
msgstr "22. Abuse"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.214:0.3"
msgid "214. Bahubhāṇisutta"
msgstr "214. Someone Who Talks a Lot"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.214:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā bahubhāṇismiṃ puggale."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks for a person who talks a lot."

msgctxt "an5.214:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.214:1.3"
msgid ""
"Musā bhaṇati, pisuṇaṃ bhaṇati, pharusaṃ bhaṇati, samphappalāpaṃ bhaṇati, "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, and nonsensical. When their "
"body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, "
"the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an5.214:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā bahubhāṇismiṃ puggale."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks for a person who talks a lot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.214:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā mantabhāṇismiṃ puggale."
msgstr "There are these five benefits for a person who talks thoughtfully."

msgctxt "an5.214:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.214:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na musā bhaṇati, na pisuṇaṃ bhaṇati, na pharusaṃ bhaṇati, na samphappalāpaṃ "
"bhaṇati, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, and nonsensical. When "
"their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a "
"heavenly realm."

msgctxt "an5.214:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā mantabhāṇismiṃ puggale”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits for a person who talks thoughtfully.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.214:2.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
